project_descr: PAL/ Rehbilitation of Municipal Infrastructure- CAP II

outputs.output_descr:
The Project will contribute to providing easier access to health and educational facilities at the town, improve the level of water availability, and reduce potential health problems through the repair of wastewater and storm water lines. In addition, the Project will enable local organizations to deliver their services to the beneficiaries such as women, children and youth. These impacts will positively affect the humanitarian activities and the overall living conditions in the targeted town of Beit Hanoun.
